{"tid":1652694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【驚人突發】 藍絲界KOL華記 踢爆謝振中為求自保向美國舉報香港警察","createTime":"2019-10-13T18:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T16:22:48.000Z","uid":219147,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc6e3157c3daea8facd736fec67d780933da3163","tid":1652694,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LMiSU4x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLMiSU4x.png&h=be3c9084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼早前有人踢爆謝振中 (謝Sir) 準備移民美國，而太太更正值坐「移民監」後，謝sir隨即放兩星期大假。而《華記正能量 Dont Worry be happy》剛發佈一段內幕消息，指出謝Sir為了挽救移民的資格，已向美國舉報香港警察 。而華記亦確認真有其事，對於出賣警隊的行為表示失望及遺憾。有網民質疑為何華記這麼激動，莫非內幕是「見光死」的駭人消息？"},{"pid":"31bd582a7d2342ef64cd67a0e04e5c3f388de1fc","tid":1652694,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:25:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37aae3a37b4e184eac7bd469fa7fa6ad182e21a6","tid":1652694,"uid":91432,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:31:46.000Z","msg":"連登仔反宣傳成功<br />\n腦生屎窟嘅藍屍的確信咗<br />\n有冇嚇到瀨尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"7a507b9c7ab0f1ae8efd09a4eddf4bbc9d8be21a","tid":1652694,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:33:16.000Z","msg":"華記正撚樣都咁講, 煲大佢啦"},{"pid":"0f716b9fac3cc5dc00485800363602377dc290d3","tid":1652694,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a507b9c7ab0f1ae8efd09a4eddf4bbc9d8be21a","tid":1652694,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:33:16.000Z","msg":"華記正撚樣都咁講, 煲大佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 华记 </span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29b26e51e48f81dc7b5d6cf2a26d34d6597c094","tid":1652694,"uid":126317,"like":0